Ranger Help for: longshot
=========================

SYNTAX:      longshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  archery

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to fire a long-range bow attack at a target.
Longshot trades speed for power, delivering a carefully aimed shot that
deals more damage than a quickshot. The SP cost varies based on the
Ranger's archery skill level and the bow used. The Ranger must have a
bow wielded and an arrow readied. Longshot is the standard ranged
attack for Rangers who prefer precision over rapid fire.
